section.section:
If the board is composed of a number evenly divisible by four (4):
One-fourth (1/4) of the board members' initial terms shall be one (1) year;
One-fourth (1/4) of the board members' initial terms shall be two (2) years;
One-fourth (1/4) of the board members' initial terms shall be three (3) years; and
One-fourth (1/4) of the board members' initial terms shall be four (4) years.
